# TeachersPet

TeachersPet is a computer-vision–based monitoring tool that detects background people
and triggers visual/audio effects when a teacher is detected. 
This alerts the currently used app if the user is doing irrelevant tasks.

---

## Requirements
- macOS / Windows
- Python 3.10 or newer
- Built in camera

---

## (macOS only) Install Homebrew
If you don’t have Homebrew installed:

```bash
/bin/bash -c "$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Homebrew/install/HEAD/install.sh)"

## for installing python packages
pip install .
